Pre-Game Insights: The Phillies have a plan in place for staying sharp during their first-round bye, including a day off, workouts, and an intrasquad scrimmage.
Nick Castellanos emphasized the importance of remaining focused during the break.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Phillies won the NL East division for the first time since 2011.
Alec Bohm, Edmundo Sosa, and Austin Hays recently came off the injured list.
Bryce Harper and J.T. Realmuto have known injuries.
